<h2>Addendum to the consequences:</h2>
</p>

<p>After Level 5, tasks become cumulative (i.e. Level 7 would have to do Level 6 and Level 5 in addition to Level 7).
</p>

<p>Each Uncompleted Task by the time of the Daily Check-In counts as a demerit each day it is left undone.  When a member accumulates two demerits, they become a Consequence, to be appended to any existing Consequences.
</p>

<p>If Level is not reconciled within one week of assignment, then consequence advances to next Level.</p>